MTQ1MiDG6ImvBjAAOA1AInIJNjQ2NzExNzgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1709346040.813208", "card_id": "Q_646614948", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 80}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "马斯克以违反合同为由起诉 OpenAI 及其 CEO 萨姆·奥特曼，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间周四晚间，特斯拉 CEO 埃隆·马斯克向旧金山高等法院提起诉讼，以违反合同为由起诉 OpenAI 及其 CEO 萨姆·奥特曼。马斯克在诉讼中表示，奥特曼和 OpenAI 违背了这家人工智能研究公司成立时达成的一项协议，即开发技术以造福人类而不是利润。马斯克声称 OpenAI 最近与科技巨头微软的关系损害了该公司致力于公共、开源的通用人工智能的初衷。马斯克说:「OpenAI 已经转变为世界上最大的科技公司微软事实上的闭源子公司。在新董事会的领导下，它不仅是在开发，而且实际上是在完善 AGI，以实现微软的利润最大化，而不是造福人类。」马斯克起诉 OpenAI 及其 CEO 奥特曼"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5ae4474f93159cc07005ab082e6475ac_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646614948"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+PWcivHi47x/EAMaCTEwNTk2OTc5OSC9nIavBjAAOJQCQCNyCTY0NjYxNDk0OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1709346040.814230", "card_id": "Q_646407301", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 65}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "天天科技革命，日日文艺复兴，AI 浪潮之下，人们该如何应对科技变革引发的焦虑感？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-44a54e8a9ee6d18c82010fa87bc5ada9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646407301"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI+PWcivHi47x/EAMaCTEwNTkyMzc1NCCa8P+uBjAAOJ4BQCRyCTY0NjQwNzMwMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1709346040.815278", "card_id": "Q_646560805", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 16}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "23-24 赛季 NBA 雷霆 118:132 马刺，如